[[["csubj", "mark", "cop", "nmod", "case", "mwe", "compound", "cc", "conj", "nsubj", "cop", "advmod"], "To forgive is divine, according to Alexander Pope, but it is hardly easy."], [["advmod", "aux", "nsubj", "dobj", "det", "acl:relcl", "nsubj", "nmod", "case", "cc", "conj", "advmod", "advmod", "conj", "det", "acl:relcl", "nsubj", "xcomp", "nsubj", "nmod:poss", "cc", "conj", "det", "amod", "cc", "conj"], "How do you forgive a driver that runs into someone and then drives away, a bully who makes your life miserable, or a cheating boyfriend or girlfriend?"], [["ccomp", "nsubj", "aux", "aux", "dobj", "nmod", "nsubj", "aux", "neg", "dobj", "advcl", "mark", "dobj", "nsubj", "nmod", "case", "advmod", "dep", "dep", "nsubjpass", "auxpass", "xcomp", "mark", "nmod", "case", "det", "amod"], "You might have had thoughts like, I can never forgive him for what he did to me. All of us are challenged to forgive on a regular basis."], [["nsubj", "nmod", "case", "ccomp", "nsubj", "aux", "cc", "conj", "nsubj", "ccomp", "mark", "nsubj", "cop", "nmod", "case", "nummod", "advmod", "mwe", "amod"], "Most of us know we should forgive, but studies show that forgiveness  is important for more than just moral reasons."], [["nsubj", "aux", "advmod", "dobj", "nmod:poss", "amod", "cc", "conj"], "It can also improve our physical and emotional health."], [["nsubj", "ccomp", "mark", "nsubj", "dobj", "conj", "cc", "conj"], "Studies show that forgiveness reduces anger, nervousness, and stress."], [["nsubj", "advmod", "nmod", "case", "nmod", "case", "conj", "cc", "conj"], "It also leads to feelings of hope, compassion, and self-confidence."], [["nsubjpass", "aux", "advmod", "auxpass", "xcomp", "mark", "ccomp", "nsubj", "compound", "advmod"], "Forgiveness has even been shown to help cancer patients live longer!"], [["csubj", "xcomp", "mark", "dep", "case", "det", "amod", "cop", "neg"], "Refusing to forgive, on the other hand, is not healthy."], [["nsubj", "aux", "dobj", "nmod:poss", "acl", "mark", "dobj", "compound", "conj", "amod", "compound", "cc", "conj"], "It can increase your risk of developing heart diseases, high blood pressure, and depression."], [["cop", "nsubj", "compound"], "What Is True Forgiveness?"], [["nsubj", "aux", "ccomp", "nmod", "case", "nmod", "case", "cc", "conj"], "Forgiveness is letting go of feelings of hurt or anger."], [["nsubj", "aux", "neg", "advmod", "xcomp"], "Forgiveness does not necessarily mean forgetting."], [["advcl", "mark", "nsubj", "det", "dobj", "nmod:poss", "nmod", "case", "advmod", "dobj", "cc", "conj", "dobj", "parataxis", "nsubj", "cop", "det", "amod", "nmod", "case", "amod", "cc", "conj", "nsubj", "amod", "cop", "advmod", "neg", "nmod", "case", "nmod:poss"], "If a friend reveals your secrets to someone else, forgive him and tell yourself: He is a good friend in other ways, but keeping secrets is currently not one of his attributes."], [["advmod", "nsubj", "advmod", "dep", "nmod", "case"], "Why Is It So Hard to Forgive?"], [["nsubj", "amod", "ccomp", "nsubj", "aux", "cc", "conj", "xcomp", "nsubj"], "Most people believe they should forgive, but find it difficult."], [["nsubj", "nmod", "case", "det", "amod", "amod", "ccomp", "mark", "nsubj", "compound", "xcomp", "mark", "dobj", "det", "nmod", "case", "det"], "One of the most common reasons is that people dont want to let the offender off the hook."], [["csubj", "dobj", "nsubj", "cop"], "What they want is justice."], [["advmod", "nsubj", "neg", "xcomp", "nsubj", "advmod", "advcl", "mark", "nsubj", "dobj", "det"], "However, not forgiving hurts you far more than it hurts the offender."], [["nsubj", "advmod", "ccomp", "nsubj", "ccomp", "nsubj", "aux", "advcl", "mark", "mwe", "nsubj", "neg", "aux", "advmod"], "People often think forgiveness means they should act as if no wrongdoing has ever happened."], [["advcl", "mark", "nsubj", "aux", "dobj", "nmod:poss", "nsubj", "aux", "cop", "dep", "neg", "mark", "dobj", "cc", "conj", "advmod"], "If someone has broken your trust, it may be wise not to trust him or her again."], [["nsubj", "cop", "advmod", "cc", "conj", "nsubj", "cop"], "Forgiveness is sometimes challenging, but it is possible."], [["ccomp", "mark", "nsubj", "cop", "neg", "det", "nmod", "case", "det"], "Remember that forgiveness is not a feeling but a choice."], [["advmod", "nsubj", "acl", "mark", "ccomp", "nsubj", "dep", "nmod", "case", "nmod:poss", "cc", "conj", "advmod"], "Here are ways to help you let go of your resentment and truly forgive:"], [["dep", "xcomp", "mark", "dobj", "det", "advcl", "mark", "nmod", "case", "nsubj", "ccomp", "nsubj", "compound:prt"], "Trying to forget the offense without dealing with it wont make it go away."], [["advmod", "xcomp", "mark", "dep", "nsubj", "advmod", "aux", "dobj", "cc", "conj"], "Instead, try to analyze exactly what is bothering you and why."], [["dobj", "det", "nmod", "case", "det", "acl:relcl", "nsubj", "dobj"], "Write a letter to the person who hurt you."], [["ccomp", "nsubj", "advmod", "aux", "dobj"], "Write exactly what is bothering you."], [["advmod", "compound:prt", "dobj", "det", "cc", "conj", "dobj", "advmod"], "Then tear up the letter and throw it away."], [["nsubj", "aux", "advmod", "advcl", "advmod", "mark", "nsubj", "det", "neg", "dobj", "det"], "You will feel better, even if the offender never sees the letter."], [["dobj", "det", "amod"], "Forgive the little things."], [["nsubj", "amod", "compound", "appos", "amod", "compound", "ccomp", "nsubj", "dobj", "amod", "nmod", "case", "amod"], "Daily troubleswunpleasant classmates, nasty bus drivers, disrespectful childrenwcan cause more stress than big offenses."], [["nsubj", "amod", "amod", "dobj", "compound:prt", "advcl", "mark", "nmod", "case", "det", "amod"], "Forgiving small things frees you up to work on the big offenses."], [["xcomp", "mark", "ccomp", "advmod", "nsubj", "det", "ccomp", "dobj", "nsubj", "cc", "conj"], "Try to understand why the offender did what he or she did."], [["nsubj", "aux", "advmod", "dobj", "det", "nmod", "case", "acl", "xcomp", "mark", "cop", "det", "cc", "conj", "advcl", "advmod", "nsubj", "dobj", "det"], "You could even write a letter to yourself, pretending to be the offender, and explain why you committed the offense."], [["nsubj", "nmod:poss", "compound", "ccomp", "advmod", "advmod", "advcl", "mark", "nsubj", "det", "cop"], "Your hurt feelings wont heal quickly, especially if the offense was serious."], [["nsubj", "dobj", "advcl", "mark", "nsubj", "aux", "compound:prt", "advmod", "advmod"], "Dont blame yourself if you cant move on right away."], [["dobj", "det", "nmod", "case", "det"], "Replace the bad with the good."], [["advcl", "mark", "advmod", "nsubj", "xcomp", "mark", "dobj", "amod", "nmod", "case", "amod"], "To really forgive, you need to replace negative emotions with positive ones."], [["xcomp", "mark", "ccomp", "cc", "conj", "nmod", "case"], "Work to replace hurt and anger with love."], [["dobj", "cc", "conj", "dobj", "xcomp", "neg", "mark", "nmod", "case", "amod", "advmod"], "Choose forgiveness, and promise yourself not to indulge in unforgiving thoughts again."], [["dobj", "det", "nmod", "case", "nmod", "case", "amod", "nmod", "case", "conj", "ccomp", "dobj", "nsubj", "aux", "cc", "conj", "case", "det"], "Write a note to yourself, with todays date on it, stating whom you have forgiven and for what offense."], [["aux", "nsubj", "dobj", "det", "amod", "advcl", "dobj", "advmod", "advmod"], "Are you having a difficult time forgiving someone right now?"], [["dobj", "det", "cc", "conj", "xcomp", "dobj", "nmod", "case", "acl", "dobj"], "Try these suggestions, and begin letting go of those hurt feelings."], [["advmod", "nsubj", "det", "cc", "conj", "amod", "dep", "det"], "Enjoy the freedom and improved health that forgiveness brings."]]